{
  "stem": "27770.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you know what it means?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not only he took them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He asked all of them, you have relatives here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In order to get from the relatives more information what's going on with this-- with this midget family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a group of 30 people, women and men, were in this group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were already in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're still alive, a few, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave-- this was the-- they say, the first time in history for Auschwitz when the gas was already on and they gave an order to stop the gas.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took them out and brought them to my barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To my barrack was taken only two.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were two men, midgets, and five women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They was with my sister in their barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We sat eight months together in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every night we was talking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They was put in [INAUDIBLE] every morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This gangster Mengele brought them in order to get more information-- brought them Friday candles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They should be able to light on candles for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, he knew it, because he wanted to get all that information out of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, he couldn't understand, how the hell is it possible when nine children, two normals and-- and seven midgets?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he started to study and dig into deeper in-- in feelings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe your mother had to do with another man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These two normal were from another man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the seven midgets were-- were from another man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So until they proved it-- that their mother and their father-- strictly religious, who never had to do with any other man and not any woman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they convinced him, you understand?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He needed all these details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He asked us a lot about the-- the Torah-- all kind of religious question.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
